A family has a right to know.<br><br>
A nation has a right to not be deceived!<br><br>
Where is the honor in the fathers of our nation.<br>
Why do they play games again and again. With less <br>
morality than a slug. They &quot;make&quot; unknown soldiers,<br>
make up excuses for war, or to support the dictators<br>
of this world, or to do anything they can get away<br>
with.  They are the criminals of the war.<br><br>
My heart go out to all of us whose sores are once again<br>
opened by this travisty of justice.<br><br>
Honor the dead with the truth. Only the truth can set<br>
us free. 
